---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hummingbird Social Studio | Downloadable Wedding Invitation Templates"
  description="Downloadable wedding invitation templates, editable wedding invitation suites, bridal shower invites, and printable wedding stationery with a soft modern style."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="eyebrow">Editable wedding templates</p>
        <h1>Beautiful wedding stationery made simple.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Hummingbird Social Studio creates downloadable wedding invitation templates, bridal shower invitations, menu cards, thank you cards, and printable wedding stationery for modern celebrations.</p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">Browse Wedding Invitations</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/">Explore Bridal Shower Invites</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Shop by category</p>
        <h2>Wedding templates for every little detail.</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/">
            <h3>Wedding Invitations</h3>
            <p>Downloadable invitation templates with matching RSVP cards, detail cards, and coordinated wedding stationery.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="/bridal-shower-invitations/">
            <h3>Bridal Shower Invitations</h3>
            <p>Pretty, easy-to-edit bridal shower invite templates for brunches, garden parties, and modern celebrations.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="/contact/">
            <h3>Custom Requests</h3>
            <p>Need a matching menu, thank you card, or wedding sign? Reach out for template questions and custom ideas.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-band">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why digital templates?</p>
        <h2>Download, edit, print, and celebrate.</h2>
        <p>Our templates are designed for couples who want polished wedding stationery without starting from scratch. Edit the wording, update your details, download your files, and print at home or through your favorite print shop.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Find us online</p>
        <h2>Shop, save, and get inspired.</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="https://www.pinterest.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <h3>Follow on Pinterest</h3>
            <p>Save wedding invitation ideas, bridal shower inspiration, color palettes, and printable stationery styles for your celebration.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="https://www.etsy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <h3>Shop on Etsy</h3>
            <p>Find downloadable Hummingbird Social Studio wedding templates, editable invitation suites, and printable celebration stationery.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="/wedding-invitation-suites/minimalist-weddings/">
            <h3>Browse Minimalist Invitations</h3>
            <p>Explore clean, simple, downloadable wedding invitation templates with an elegant modern feel.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
